title: ‘The Challenge: All Stars’ Season 2 With Darrell | Death, Taxes, and Bananas
description:
Johnny is taking a quick break from 'Spies, Lies, and Allies' to bring you seasoned veteran Darrell Taylor's perspective on Season 2 of 'The Challenge: All Stars.' They discuss the differences between the flagship show and 'All Stars,' drama from past seasons, the absolutely draining deliberation between Darrell and Tina on the most recent episode of 'All Stars,' and much more.
Host: Johnny Bananas
Guest: Darrell Taylor
Associate Producer: Sasha Ashall
Additional Production: Juliet Litman
